<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 22:06:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡表示，哈马斯战争后，以色列将接管加沙的安全控制权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-israel-will-assume-security-control-over-gaza-following-hamas-war/0000018b-bad5-dedf-adab-ffd5cae10000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡告诉以色列南部社区的负责人，该计划还包括加沙非军事化，以确保它不再对以色列公民构成威胁</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 21:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-israel-will-assume-security-control-over-gaza-following-hamas-war/0000018b-bad5-dedf-adab-ffd5cae10000</guid></item><item><title>暂时停火？不，以色列必须镇压哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/temporary-cease-fire-no-israel-must-crush-hamas/0000018b-ba78-dea2-a9bf-fafe88cf0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 21:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/temporary-cease-fire-no-israel-must-crush-hamas/0000018b-ba78-dea2-a9bf-fafe88cf0000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚两个带头反以色列抗议活动的亲巴勒斯坦团体被暂停</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/two-pro-palestinian-groups-spearheading-anti-israel-protests-at-columbia-suspended/0000018b-bae1-d03e-a3ab-bbfd039a0000</link><description>哥伦比亚大学暂停巴勒斯坦正义学生组织和犹太和平之声组织的活动，因为这些组织“多次违反大学有关举办校园活动的政策”，并举办了一场包括“威胁言论和恐吓”的活动</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 20:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/two-pro-palestinian-groups-spearheading-anti-israel-protests-at-columbia-suspended/0000018b-bae1-d03e-a3ab-bbfd039a0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷法院因发表反对以色列-哈马斯战争的帖子而延长历史教师的还押期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-court-extends-remand-of-history-teacher-over-posts-against-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-b9ab-dedf-adab-fdbbb90a0000</link><description>法官在判决中引用了老师的帖子，其中称“我们杰出的男孩”在约旦河西岸处决了两名巴勒斯坦人，并补充说“他们从来不知道有一天会有真正的自由”</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 18:36:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-court-extends-remand-of-history-teacher-over-posts-against-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-b9ab-dedf-adab-fdbbb90a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙城内与哈马斯作战，否认对希法医院发动空袭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-live/soldier-killed-in-northern-gaza-israel-attacks-in-syria-in-response-to-eilat-drone-strike/0000018b-b76c-df42-a78f-bf6fd3470000</link><description>马克龙：以色列继续轰炸加沙妇女和婴儿是“没有道理的” ■ 五名士兵被黎巴嫩飞机的反坦克导弹炸伤，其中四人重伤 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：击败哈马斯后，加沙将继续处于以色列安全控制之下 ■ 以色列国防军名称另有两名士兵在加沙战斗中丧生 ■ 以色列国防军：杀死了领导 10 月 7 日大屠杀的哈马斯精锐指挥官 ■ 拜登确认以色列同意每天暂停战斗 4 小时 ■ 哈马斯大屠杀至少造成 1,300 人死亡，239 名人质在加沙被扣，40 人下落不明■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：自战斗开始以来已有 11,078 人死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 18:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-live/soldier-killed-in-northern-gaza-israel-attacks-in-syria-in-response-to-eilat-drone-strike/0000018b-b76c-df42-a78f-bf6fd3470000</guid></item><item><title>加沙官员：以色列空袭希法医院和学校附近，造成约22人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/gaza-officials-22-people-killed-as-israeli-airstrikes-hit-near-shifa-hospital-school/0000018b-ba1b-d03e-a3ab-bbbff1ee0000</link><description>加沙官员表示，周五以色列空袭袭击了加沙地带的三家医院和一所学校，而另一家医院的地面战斗仍在继续</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 17:19:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/gaza-officials-22-people-killed-as-israeli-airstrikes-hit-near-shifa-hospital-school/0000018b-ba1b-d03e-a3ab-bbbff1ee0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯人反对战争的声音是民主的声音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/the-voice-of-israeli-arabs-opposing-the-war-is-the-voice-of-democracy/0000018b-b985-df42-a78f-bdc78d6d0000</link><description>大多数阿拉伯国家的回应集中在呼吁不要集体惩罚200万不支持哈马斯的加沙人。如果华盛顿和柏林的人们能够抗议千里之外正在发生的事情，那么在拿撒勒和乌姆法姆举行集会当然应该被允许</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 15:19:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/the-voice-of-israeli-arabs-opposing-the-war-is-the-voice-of-democracy/0000018b-b985-df42-a78f-bdc78d6d0000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡现在必须下台”：以色列新近失去亲人的家人要求一名男子负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/netanyahu-must-go-now-israels-newly-bereaved-families-are-holding-one-man-responsible/0000018b-b94e-d03e-a3ab-bbffcf020000</link><description>事情发生在上周六。在哈马斯袭击中失去亲人的家庭聚集在耶路撒冷，拆除了他们和内塔尼亚胡住所之间的障碍。他们的火山般的愤怒开始爆发。他们再也无法忍受这个人仍然是首相的事实</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 14:43:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/netanyahu-must-go-now-israels-newly-bereaved-families-are-holding-one-man-responsible/0000018b-b94e-d03e-a3ab-bbffcf020000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的人道主义危机变成以色列的战略武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/gazas-humanitarian-crisis-turns-into-a-strategic-weapon-for-israel/0000018b-b931-d03e-a3ab-bbbd43530000</link><description>加沙的人道主义危机现在为以色列提供了外交影响力，其中包括获得埃及的让步以及阻止美国急于达成两国解决方案</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 13:29:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/gazas-humanitarian-crisis-turns-into-a-strategic-weapon-for-israel/0000018b-b931-d03e-a3ab-bbbd43530000</guid></item><item><title>数百人恳求我将他们从哈马斯狂欢大屠杀中拯救出来。我该怎么办？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hundreds-begged-me-to-save-them-from-the-rave-attack-what-was-i-to-do/0000018b-b8ef-dea2-a9bf-f8ff5a690000</link><description>国土报的警察和犯罪记者收到了大量逃离袭击雷伊姆音乐节的哈马斯恐怖分子的信息。由于迫切需要帮助，他将这些信息的位置直接转发给以色列警察局长，后者敦促他继续发送这些信息。直到本周他才能重新阅读这些信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 12:55:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hundreds-begged-me-to-save-them-from-the-rave-attack-what-was-i-to-do/0000018b-b8ef-dea2-a9bf-f8ff5a690000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争爆发以来，八名以色列犹太人被指控犯有种族主义暴力行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/eight-israeli-jews-charged-with-racist-violence-since-start-of-gaza-war/0000018b-b8f1-d03e-a3ab-bbfdc0c20000</link><description>自10月7日以来，已有60多名以色列阿拉伯人被指控犯有此类罪行，这也标志着因类似嫌疑而逮捕和调查以色列阿拉伯人的数量激增</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 12:22:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/eight-israeli-jews-charged-with-racist-violence-since-start-of-gaza-war/0000018b-b8f1-d03e-a3ab-bbfdc0c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称，袭击以色列最南端城市埃拉特的无人机来自叙利亚；以色列国防军进行报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-drone-struck-israels-southernmost-city-came-from-syria-idf-retaliates/0000018b-b8ba-df42-a78f-bdfb86c60000</link><description>以色列军队表示，在分析显示其射程不及来自也门的范围后，它袭击了那些对这次袭击负责的人。对无人机袭击照片碎片的检查表明，这是一架伊朗制造的 Shahed-101 或类似品牌</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 11:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-drone-struck-israels-southernmost-city-came-from-syria-idf-retaliates/0000018b-b8ba-df42-a78f-bdfb86c60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列媒体“监管机构”表示，这只是对摄影师和哈马斯的影射“提出质疑”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-media-watchdog-says-it-was-just-raising-questions-on-photographers-hamas-link/0000018b-b88c-dedf-adab-fd9cfae90000</link><description>该组织的执行董事声称，“一些有目的的人”让该组织看起来很糟糕。他说，尽管名称为“诚实报道”，但“我们并不声称自己是一家新闻机构”</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 10:31:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-media-watchdog-says-it-was-just-raising-questions-on-photographers-hamas-link/0000018b-b88c-dedf-adab-fd9cfae90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高警察警告本-格维尔大规模分发武器可能会让武器落入坏人之手</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-cop-warns-ben-gvirs-mass-weapons-distribution-could-put-them-in-wrong-hands/0000018b-b85c-dea2-a9bf-f8ded92c0000</link><description>警方官员表示，“在一片恐慌中，他们向任何人分发武器，战后要收起这些武器并不容易”，并补充说：“我们最终可能会付出沉重的代价：受伤、武器盗窃和未经检查的使用”</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 09:47:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-cop-warns-ben-gvirs-mass-weapons-distribution-could-put-them-in-wrong-hands/0000018b-b85c-dea2-a9bf-f8ded92c0000</guid></item><item><title>电影制片人猛烈抨击世界最大的纪录片节，呼吁消灭以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/filmmakers-slam-worlds-largest-documentary-fest-for-applauding-call-to-wipe-out-israel/0000018b-b86f-dea2-a9bf-f8ff29e10000</link><description>亲巴勒斯坦活动人士冲上舞台，赢得了观众和电影节艺术总监的掌声。一位以色列电影制片人表示，“他们对消灭以色列的呼吁表示欢迎，这并不是解决冲突或将巴勒斯坦人从哈马斯手中解放出来”</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 09:15:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/filmmakers-slam-worlds-largest-documentary-fest-for-applauding-call-to-wipe-out-israel/0000018b-b86f-dea2-a9bf-f8ff29e10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-哈马斯战争：以色列国防军表示需要数月时间，美国表示不超过几周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/washington-balks-at-israeli-armys-months-long-plan-to-complete-goals-in-gaza-fighting/0000018b-b539-dea2-a9bf-f5bf64530000</link><description>哈马斯陷入困境，但远未崩溃 ■ 针对以色列飞行员的煽动活动导致坠机事件 ■ 一名倒下的以色列军官的故事凸显了以色列民族国家法的问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 04:00:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/washington-balks-at-israeli-armys-months-long-plan-to-complete-goals-in-gaza-fighting/0000018b-b539-dea2-a9bf-f5bf64530000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡为生存而战，抗议团体转向确保他战后下台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahu-battles-for-survival-protest-groups-pivot-to-ensuring-his-post-war-ouster/0000018b-b5cd-dedf-adab-f5dd5b460000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡正在为他的生存之战做准备，这并不奇怪，但现在，一旦加沙战争结束，抗议他计划中的司法政变的团体将寻求他的辞职</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 04:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahu-battles-for-survival-protest-groups-pivot-to-ensuring-his-post-war-ouster/0000018b-b5cd-dedf-adab-f5dd5b460000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-10/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-b6a6-df42-a78f-bfe7c0f60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 00:40:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-10/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-b6a6-df42-a78f-bfe7c0f60000</guid></item><item><title>“对我来说，作为一名犹太人，当出现问题时就来到以色列”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-10/ty-article/.highlight/for-me-being-a-jew-is-coming-to-israel-when-there-are-problems/0000018b-b693-dea2-a9bf-f69f37760000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名犹太裔法国外科医生抵达以色列在战争期间担任志愿者，一名以色列托儿所学校老板前往格鲁吉亚实现长期以来的梦想</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 00:38:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-10/ty-article/.highlight/for-me-being-a-jew-is-coming-to-israel-when-there-are-problems/0000018b-b693-dea2-a9bf-f69f37760000</guid></item><item><title>加沙只有一种可行的战后战略，但内塔尼亚胡还有其他计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theres-only-one-viable-postwar-strategy-for-gaza-but-netanyahu-has-other-plans/0000018b-b611-df42-a78f-bf53a5080000</link><description>真正的战斗正在耶路撒冷进行，而不是加沙。以色列主流和拜登政府认识到，唯一合理的行动方针是解散哈马斯并将加沙的管理权移交给国际部队和巴勒斯坦权力机构。内塔尼亚胡和弥赛亚右派不同意</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 00:10:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theres-only-one-viable-postwar-strategy-for-gaza-but-netanyahu-has-other-plans/0000018b-b611-df42-a78f-bf53a5080000</guid></item></channel></rss>